                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>• Adults who volunteer as student mentors deepen their engagement in the learning community and realize their potential to effect positive change.

• Mentors acquire new insights and understanding about young people and the institute community, thereby contributing to broader goals of community cohesion and regeneration.</Value>
