                <TablixRow>
                  <Height>6.57958cm</Height>
                  <TablixCells>
                    <TablixCell>
                      <CellContents>
                        <Textbox Name="Textbox1040">
                          <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
                          <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
                          <Paragraphs>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>…………………………………………………………………………………………… (College/Department)</Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>Teerthanker Mahaveer University, Moradabad.</Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>
Subject: - Undertaking for maintaining 75% attendance.</Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                    <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>
Respected Sir/Madam,</Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>
This is to state that I, …………………………………………………………………………………………………………… and my father/mother Sh./Smt. …………………………………………………………………………………………..  have complete knowledge about the Teerthanker Mahaveer University Ordinance governing the attendance of students, according to which I have to attend at least 75% of the classes individually in each course/paper during the entire semester/year of the programme; failing which I will not be allowed to appear in internal and/or external examinations of the
university college/department in the course/paper(s) wherein my attendance is less than 75%.</Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>
It would be my personal responsibility to ensure 75% attendance separately in each course/paper during the programme otherwise I shall have no right/claim to appear in the internal and/or external examinations of the university in the course/paper(s) less than 75% attendance.</Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>
I assure you that I will abide by all university/college/department rules and regulations as applicable from time to time. I further, undertake that it shall be my responsibility to inform my parents regarding my short attendance as mentioned above. </Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value />
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>I am signing this undertaking after reading the University Ordinance on attendance and other matters.</Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style>
                                <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
                              </Style>
                            </Paragraph>
                          </Paragraphs>
                          <rd:DefaultName>Textbox1040</rd:DefaultName>
                          <Style>
                            <Border>
                              <Style>None</Style>
                            </Border>
                            <PaddingLeft>2pt</PaddingLeft>
                            <PaddingRight>2pt</PaddingRight>
                            <PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop>
                            <PaddingBottom>2pt</PaddingBottom>
                          </Style>
                        </Textbox>
                        <ColSpan>14</ColSpan>
                      </CellContents>
